Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.57,0:47:52.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}第一次  對自己說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.43,0:47:56.96,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}第二次  胸口作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.21,0:48:01.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}所以第三次
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.96,0:48:06.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}便裝作沒有發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.98,0:48:13.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}這樣也無所謂  已經沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.03,0:48:20.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}即便我不再是我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.25,0:48:23.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}軟弱又膽怯的Braveheart
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.96,0:48:26.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我害怕受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.33,0:48:30.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}啊  只要笑就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.84,0:48:33.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}抱持著若有若無的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.45,0:48:35.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}只能閉著眼前進
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.98,0:48:41.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}啊  即使知道這是無謀
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.04,0:48:46.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}被後悔步步緊逼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.48,0:48:51.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}快點快點逃開才行
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.19,0:48:55.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}所以我拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.04,0:49:01.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}曾經最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.03,0:49:07.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}至今才發現  一直只是活著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.06,0:49:14.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我的價值也只是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.27,0:49:17.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}虛有其名的Braveheart
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.89,0:49:20.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}根本不會有任何用
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.34,0:49:24.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}啊  即使這樣卻仍在悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.90,0:49:27.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}要對生命渴求些什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.53,0:49:29.69,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}震顫的心臟快要破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.93,0:49:39.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}啊  為了活著毫無辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.98,0:49:56.48,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.89,0:50:27.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}明明並不感到悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.51,0:50:29.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}淚水卻奪眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.91,0:50:36.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}啊  為何會如此溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.83,0:50:39.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.68,0:50:44.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}告訴了我的Braveheart
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.30,0:50:46.52,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}即使已經變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.70,0:50:51.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}啊  抱歉這都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.23,0:50:53.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}懷抱著全部的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.88,0:50:56.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}張開眼睛看著前方
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.38,0:51:05.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}啊  世界是如此耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.83,0:51:10.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}來吧  已經可以歡笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.47,0:51:13.02,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}緊握不認輸的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.17,0:51:15.50,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不用懼怕受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.57,0:51:23.27,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)}看  這就是我的Braveheart
