Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  今天怎麼起得那麼早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  比鬧鐘起得還早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能一直這個樣子就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙好燙好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了去把小博叫起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？不要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去叫了他也不會起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是姐姐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了哦  新學期哦  快點起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡過頭我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我可是來叫過你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有個地方要繞路去下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出席你的開學典禮  真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  電車電車…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開學典禮將在初中部體育館進行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各班按順序進場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照學號順序迅速入座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准閒聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有作為一個本校中學生的自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外中途要是有同學身體不適的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻告訴身邊的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}開學典禮的流程請參照手邊的小冊子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位新同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你們入學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也由衷祝賀各位家長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有對於各位來賓…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  身高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真高呢  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  剛才我看到你是坐車來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真的有這樣的人呢我好激動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我說過不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但父親無論如何都要送
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有今天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家就在附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在町並町
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  那就在我家附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是從木幡車站坐電車來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們是鄰居呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我也會從那個車站來上學的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你小學是在哪裡讀的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是之前剛剛搬家過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果附近有家小鳥遊這樣稀奇的姓的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp13}鷹無
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(314,327)}Taka Nashi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀作鷹無  寫作小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(284,327)\fsp-0.5}Taka Nashi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  為什麼會讀鷹無？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(378,327)\fsp-0.5}Taka Nashi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小鳥會玩耍的地方不會有老鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不錯的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一般都不會讀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊  小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的全名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫黑衣真透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我真透就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  不錯的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  真透…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  搬家前住在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的歸國子女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會說德語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在德國的時間很短
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說看  說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也剛來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天明明我沒繞路直接來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在考慮  真透呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籃球部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就決定升初中了就要打籃球的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  黃泉也來打籃球吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個子又那麼高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個正是我的煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很羨慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我比較矮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想如果打籃球的話說不定會長高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我選籃球部的一個理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還有其他的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也不是什麼重要理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉擅長的科目是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是英語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是啦  和德語完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說不上擅長  但是比較喜歡數學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真有喜歡數學的人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透呢  擅長什麼科目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢  今後正要去發現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在除了最好的體育以外其他都差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你技術不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前打過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  小學的時候經常在公園裡和男生一起打
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  各位繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也借我抄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下節課我那列很有可能會被點到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不自己做的話掌握不了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  愛死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  真透  好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定要進的社團了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是籃球部  不過也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的球感不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:16:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一起去逛逛？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是做姐姐的沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連黃泉都和媽媽說一樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡打來的  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  嗯  媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在？  和真透在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個地方想帶你去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我最喜歡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在這裡眺望城鎮總覺得能讓人精神百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是因為景色好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…好難說明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是有這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透很喜歡這個城鎮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是我出生成長的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小就不斷搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想黃泉離開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  希望能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛吧  在剛才的店裡買的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看  黃泉的手機上什麼都沒掛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機也會寂寞的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也掛著這樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我中意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  我會好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:22:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:22:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落地時扭到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍忍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  讓你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  只是輕微扭傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經讓優秀的經紀人護理過了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.87,0:23:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是優秀的經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該很快就會痊癒的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但暫時還是不能瞎跑亂跳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天洗澡也盡快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓腳受熱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的社團活得看情況了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  不要哎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.04,0:23:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要聽話啊  受期待的一年級王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個太羞人了  別這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我還有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.45,0:24:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.19,0:24:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級王牌嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.36,0:24:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過春季的大賽說不定會讓我出場
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.00,0:24:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  那要努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.09,0:24:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.05,0:24:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班級分開了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.92,0:24:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.65,0:24:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過教室也是相鄰的  社團活動也是一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.84,0:24:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.89,0:24:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息時就能見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.82,0:24:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.63,0:24:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.12,0:24:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.66,0:25:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新班級如何
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.78,0:25:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.21,0:25:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.47,0:25:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還沒有升上二年級的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.01,0:25:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看  等社團來了新人就會有感覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.57,0:25:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.59,0:25:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有點長高了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.16,0:25:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.71,0:25:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還遠遠追不上你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.17,0:25:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.33,0:25:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.28,0:25:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉不要再長高了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.48,0:25:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.14,0:25:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.56,0:25:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小優
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.77,0:25:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天社團活動前要開會
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.15,0:25:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別遲到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.71,0:25:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼會？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.19,0:25:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招收一年級新生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.90,0:26:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有潛力的一年級新生可不能讓排球部什麼的搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.62,0:26:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此部長已經熱血沸騰了

Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.63,0:26:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊黃泉  她叫小優
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.71,0:26:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識吧  籃球部的經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.67,0:26:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次跟我分到同一個班了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.65,0:26:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教  小鳥遊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.70,0:26:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以也叫你黃泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.15,0:26:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.91,0:26:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK  你也叫我小優就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.37,0:26:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.94,0:26:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  加油上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.31,0:26:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下來我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.48,0:26:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.46,0:26:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.72,0:26:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天社團活動結束之後山村前輩的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.45,0:26:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.86,0:26:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想用跳箱的起跳板練習灌籃
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.86,0:26:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.56,0:26:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.50,0:26:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.25,0:27:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛說到山村前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.28,0:27:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長告訴我的時候  我眼淚都快要笑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.09,0:27:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著籃球起跳的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.88,0:27:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果進籃的不是球而是自己的頭  真是個好球
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.64,0:27:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼跳的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.48,0:27:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著頭倒插進籃筐的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.91,0:27:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就笑得前仰後合
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.66,0:27:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差點笑破肚皮
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.29,0:27:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩人還是不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.15,0:27:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就是偶爾會做些匪夷所思的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.77,0:27:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.81,0:27:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長講得也很生動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.54,0:27:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了一定會發笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.22,0:27:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.03,0:27:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.38,0:27:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的話就沒法把山村前輩的事蹟講得那麼有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.43,0:27:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.40,0:27:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.72,0:27:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  黃泉不知道籃球部的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.77,0:27:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.02,0:27:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.23,0:28:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是發了下呆而已
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.83,0:28:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.85,0:28:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.91,0:28:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.37,0:28:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.97,0:30:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.31,0:30:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.39,0:30:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  部長太能說了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.49,0:30:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看見黃泉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.58,0:30:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.38,0:30:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.93,0:30:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說今天有要事所以先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.86,0:31:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉居然沒跟你說  看來事情一定很急
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.23,0:31:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不像你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.36,0:31:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.97,0:31:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.81,0:31:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.50,0:31:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.11,0:32:13.49,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(78,79)\frz14\be1\fad(0,300)}今天怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.11,0:32:13.49,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(19,121)\frz14\be1\fad(0,300)}一聲不吭的  我很擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.11,0:32:13.49,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(5,156)\frz14\be1\fad(0,300)}不過別擔心  我不會放在心上的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.11,0:32:13.49,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(128,150)\frz14\be1\fad(0,300)}明天見！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.13,0:32:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  吃飯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.62,0:32:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.29,0:33:42.33,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(219,112)\frz14\be1\fs8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.10,0:33:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.45,0:34:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道黃泉她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.75,0:34:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.05,0:34:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來她休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.43,0:34:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學的話  跟你關係不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.56,0:34:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發個短信問問吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.32,0:34:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…說得對…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.16,0:34:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立  敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.13,0:34:34.63,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,194)\frz80\be1\fs18}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.64,0:34:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(致真透  今天放學之後馬上聯繫)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.64,0:34:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(小鳥遊)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.14,0:34:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(警察)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.15,0:34:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(失蹤了)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.56,0:35:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.30,0:35:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.98,0:35:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生在樓上等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.22,0:35:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母親應該打電話告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.29,0:35:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊黃泉的父母已經提出對黃泉的搜索請求
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.81,0:35:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報案時間是昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.83,0:35:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天早上上學之後直到深夜黃泉還沒有回家
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過調查  確認她在傍晚離開了學校
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.47,0:35:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻不知道之後的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.89,0:35:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在懷疑是捲入了什麼事件當中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.42,0:36:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是出自本人意願的失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.38,0:36:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是普通的離家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.16,0:36:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還不能下定論
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.44,0:36:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.29,0:36:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉她是不會離家出走的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.81,0:36:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她的父母也是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.74,0:36:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一點頭緒也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.82,0:36:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不怕一萬就怕萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.77,0:36:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你是跟黃泉最要好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.16,0:36:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會去的地方  動機  什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.74,0:36:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼頭緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.77,0:36:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.02,0:36:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.35,0:36:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉她
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.43,0:36:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常都是跟我一起回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.81,0:36:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天卻沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.39,0:36:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排球部的人說她有急事先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.79,0:36:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發短信過去…卻沒有回信…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.22,0:37:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有沒有其他奇怪的表現？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.07,0:37:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校裡  你看  例如在休息的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.14,0:39:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說小鳥遊的事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.10,0:39:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道知道  聽說她失蹤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.00,0:39:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是綁架？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.16,0:39:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是離家出走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.38,0:39:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像個大小姐  也許家裡很有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.65,0:39:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.33,0:39:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是新聞上好像還沒提到
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.97,0:39:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不刺激犯人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.72,0:39:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  我也要小心點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.87,0:39:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家也那麼有錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.49,0:39:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.25,0:39:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就用不著擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.23,0:40:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.89,0:40:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉很快就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.21,0:40:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有什麼隱情
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.05,0:40:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會以為是自己的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.23,0:40:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.13,0:40:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也別整天愁眉苦臉的了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.81,0:40:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透不開心的話連我也會變得消極
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.18,0:40:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籃球部的夥伴們也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.63,0:40:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在擔心黃泉的同時也在擔心真透啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.87,0:40:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.90,0:40:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.93,0:40:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是黃泉回來了發現你更讓人擔心多不好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.52,0:40:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我們能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.80,0:40:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是打起精神  堅信她一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.37,0:40:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.61,0:40:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你  小優
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.09,0:40:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事  社團活動要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.80,0:40:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.93,0:41:34.64,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(306,223)\frz-22\be1\fs28}黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.79,0:41:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉！?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.31,0:41:39.77,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304,111)\frz3\fs18}黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.31,0:41:39.77,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,135)\frz3\fs20}無
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.61,0:41:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.47,0:41:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.61,0:42:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.11,0:42:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說真透  你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.03,0:42:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.16,0:42:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去黃泉那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.58,0:43:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.31,0:43:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡啊
